description: Live atop the Seaport! A special opportunity to own the Penthouse with the LARGEST terrace at EchelonSeaport.  This 2BR and 2.5BA with a 768 sq ft private terrace with gas and water hookup is perfect for entertaining! Upgraded finishes include: gas fireplace, wide plank ivory oak floors throughout, Gaggenau appliances with gas cooking, custom Italian cabinetry, floor to ceiling windows framing 180 degree views. EchelonSeaport features the largest residential amenity space in Boston with over 50,000 SF!  Enjoy the indoor pool year round, 2 outdoor swimming pools with hot tub, indoor basketball court, sports simulator, yoga room and gym.  Enjoy fall evenings with outdoor fire pits and grilling kitchens!  Professionally designed by award winning interior designers Kohn Pederson Fox other extensions of your home include private dining space, Sky lounge, and library.  Beautifully designed paired with exceptional services such as 24/7 concierge services, valet parking and porters.
